  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Representative (FMCG)",
  "description": "<p>If you are passionate about sales or meet people, we welcome you to join our growing team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Account Sales Representative (FMCG)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Main Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Visit retail outlets, wholesalers, and distributors regularly to generate sales</li>\n  <li>Manage and grow key modern trade accounts (Supermarket/retail or convenience store, etc)</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain strong working relationships with buyers and retail partners</li>\n  <li>Execute sales strategies to meet or exceed targets</li>\n  <li>Fast response to market needs by monitoring and track competitors’ activities</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate records of sales, customer interactions, and market feedback</li>\n  <li>Participate in promotional activities and involve in marketing events</li>\n  <li>Ensure product visibility and availability in key outlets</li>\n  <li>Work closely with internal operations/ logistic teams to ensure smooth order fulfillment</li>\n  <li>Provide weekly &amp; monthly sales reports to management</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent after-sales service to maintain customer satisfaction and repeat business</li>\n  <li>Stay up to date with industry regulations and product developments</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Who We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<p>· Min 1-2 years relevant experience, preferably in FMCG line</p>\n<p>· Well-presented, professional, and business savvy.</p>\n<p>· Good communication skills</p>\n<p>· Strong interpersonal and negotiation skills.</p>\n<p>· Detail-oriented, “Hunter” mindset and result-driven</p>\n<p>· Self-motivated, proactive with initiative</p>\n<p>· Immediate availability or short notice preferred</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you meet the above, we welcome you to send in your detailed resume to hr@puricare.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>",
